---
// Banner provisional para mostrar estado de AutoMatch
---

<div class="automatch-banner">
  <div class="banner-content">
    <div class="banner-icon">🚀</div>
    <div class="banner-text">
      <h3>AutoMatch - Fase Inicial</h3>
      <p>
        Estamos mejorando nuestro algoritmo de recomendaciones con datos reales
        de concesionarios. Prueba la herramienta y ayúdanos a perfeccionarla.
      </p>
    </div>
    <button
      class="banner-close"
      onclick="this.parentElement.parentElement.style.display='none'"
    >
      ✕
    </button>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .automatch-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1b5e3f 0%, #08341f 100%);
    border-left: 4px solid #25d366;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    animation: slideIn 0.4s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes slideIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .banner-content {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .banner-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .banner-text {
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  .banner-text h3 {
    color: #25d366;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-family: "Georgia", serif;
  }

  .banner-text p {
    color: #ccc;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .banner-close {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: #25d366;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .banner-close:hover {
    background: rgba(37, 211, 102, 0.1);
    transform: scale(1.15);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .automatch-banner {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .banner-content {
      gap: 1rem;
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .banner-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .banner-text h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .banner-text p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
